main event: A unidentified object was spotted flying over Culebra Island in the Caribbean at a high speed and altitude.
interesting points: The object was described as metallic and triangular-shaped.
The object flew level and then descended.
The object made 3 turns and then descended.
A pilot in a Piper Apache aircraft also reported seeing a rocket or missile flying at high speed over the island.
The sighting lasted for over 1 hour.
photographs: no photographs included in the report
